description:
During its run in Chicago, I had the chance to check out The Lord of the Rings: A Musical Tale.  We went behind the scenes to check out some of the effects, chat with some of the actors, and enjoy the show!

Check out https://lotrmusical.com/ for more info!

#lordoftherings #theatre #behindthescenes
title: Behind the Scenes with The Lord of the Rings Musical!
